Smallest unit of programming language is token.
keywords are predefined words.
variables are the container  which store  some values and variables are changable.
constants are the container  but we cant change the value  and are unchangable.
Datatype : type of data : number, String , boolean, undefined, null, BigInt, Symbol.
Node js is  a runtime environment.
Functionn is  a block of code which is used to perform a specific task.


Important! => What is IIFE function: Stands for Immidiate invoke function expression, it is usually written in same line or  we can call it inline function.
Important!.

Can't make an arrow function a  IIFE function.
3 types of logical operator : && , || , !.
var is a window object that is it is global scope.
let have a local scope.
alert is used for  pop up data in a web.
when this is used it referce to  the window  itself if not pointing to a fucntion.
higher order function:  higher order function ability of the function to accept another  function as a parameter.
call back function :   the function that is passed as a parameter in a function is known as  cbf.
Dom is document object model  that is a hierarchichal structure of a html document.
